channel.title: Cant log onto my server
channel.description: I am trying to run a varrockscape server at the moment, I havent modified it or anything, just trying to logon, but i cant. On the server prompt it shows me trying to log on, then it says logged out a second later. I tried to run a server with a different base before, and I had a similar problem, except it just said something like Client null disconnected instead. I've searched the forums for that error, except nothing I have found helps me solve my problem.
